      <title>越南前副部长等 15 人因涉嫌石油公司贿赂案受审</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/vietnam-ex-deputy-minister-among-15-in-oil-firm-bribery-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南前贸易部副部长和前省委书记因涉嫌与一家石油公司有关的贿赂指控于周三在胡志明市开庭审理，这是这个东南亚共产主义国家持续铲除腐败运动的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/vietnam-ex-deputy-minister-among-15-in-oil-firm-bribery-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 08:53:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌干达反对党领袖贝西杰的妻子称其在肯尼亚“被绑架”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/uganda-opposition-leader-besigye-kidnapped-in-kenya-wife-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据乌干达反对派领导人基扎·贝西杰 (Kizza Besigye) 的妻子称，他上周末在邻国肯尼亚首都被拘留，并被转移到坎帕拉，目前被关押在军事监狱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/uganda-opposition-leader-besigye-kidnapped-in-kenya-wife-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 08:53:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>桥水基金称特朗普可能会选择更为包容的美联储主席</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/bridgewater-says-trump-may-pick-more-accommodating-fed-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[桥水基金联席首席投资官鲍勃·普林斯周三表示，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的关税、财政刺激和移民政策可能会导致美国无法实现 2% 的通胀目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/bridgewater-says-trump-may-pick-more-accommodating-fed-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 08:13:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰称支持发行欧洲联合债券以资助国防</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/poland-says-backs-joint-european-bonds-to-finance-defense</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰外交部长拉多斯瓦夫·西科尔斯基表示，波兰支持发行欧洲联合债券为国防开支融资的倡议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/poland-says-backs-joint-european-bonds-to-finance-defense</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 08:10:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石破茂承诺进行税收谈判，刺激计划获批</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/japan-s-stimulus-package-gets-dpp-nod-with-tax-talk-inclusion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本国民民主党高级官员滨口诚称，日本首相石破茂与主要反对党就经济刺激方案达成协议，承诺将把讨论反对党的减税提案纳入其中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/japan-s-stimulus-package-gets-dpp-nod-with-tax-talk-inclusion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 06:54:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税计划或将对泰国经济造成 46 亿美元冲击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/thai-economy-seen-taking-4-6-billion-hit-from-trump-tariff-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项研究表明，如果当选总统唐纳德·特朗普履行承诺提高美国进口商品关税，泰国明年可能无法实现其增长目标，因为这可能会损害这个东南亚国家的出口并削弱其货币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/thai-economy-seen-taking-4-6-billion-hit-from-trump-tariff-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 06:46:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾部长访问布鲁塞尔，无视中国孤立主义的举措</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/taiwan-minister-kicks-off-europe-trip-with-stop-in-brussels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾外交部长林家龙为期一周的欧洲之行首先在布鲁塞尔停留，此行体现了台北与其他民主国家建立联系的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/taiwan-minister-kicks-off-europe-trip-with-stop-in-brussels</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 03:38:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里约混乱表明特朗普回归前世界就已经失去控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/chaos-in-rio-shows-a-world-untethered-even-before-trump-returns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[凯匹林纳鸡尾酒在流淌，桑巴舞和弗雷沃舞者在摇摆，轻柔的海风笼罩着里约热内卢的贵宾。但随着二十国集团公报在网上出现，气氛却远非喜庆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/chaos-in-rio-shows-a-world-untethered-even-before-trump-returns</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 23:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其希望特朗普解决 S-400 争端并购买 F-35</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/turkey-pins-hopes-on-trump-to-resolve-s-400-feud-and-buy-f-35s</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在等待总统乔·拜登采取行动多年后，土耳其将希望寄托在当选总统唐纳德·特朗普身上，希望他能解除因使用俄罗斯防空系统而受到的制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/turkey-pins-hopes-on-trump-to-resolve-s-400-feud-and-buy-f-35s</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 19:34:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
